A Chrome extension that warns you of angry email drafts using the Google Cloud Natural Language API.

Deepbreath does not collect any user data, but does send it to the Google Cloud Natural Language API. See Google Cloud's privacy policy here:

https://cloud.google.com/terms/data-processing-terms
